<taxonomicName authorityName="Ho" authorityYear="2019" baseAuthorityName="Pic" baseAuthorityYear="1934" box="[375,573,1858,1882]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Pygoluciola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="141" pageNumber="142" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vitalisi" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis box="[375,573,1858,1882]" italics="true" pageId="141" pageNumber="142">Pygoluciola vitalisi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[580,697,1858,1882]" pageId="141" pageNumber="142">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[580,697,1858,1882]" pageId="141" pageNumber="142" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
males. 456 habitus dorsal; 457 habitus ventral; 458, 461, 462 aedeagus: 458 left lateral; 461 ventral; 462 dorsal; 459, 469 aedeagal sheath: 459 ventral (with aedeagus); 460 ventral without aedeagus. Scale lines are 1 mm.
</paragraph>
